especially heinous.

00:06.574 --> 00:09.543
In New York City,
the dedicated detectives

00:09.577 --> 00:11.179
who investigate
these vicious felonies

00:11.212 --> 00:12.713
are members of an elite squad

00:12.746 --> 00:14.582
known as
the Special Victims Unit.

00:14.615 --> 00:17.251
These are their stories.

00:19.587 --> 00:22.323
Multiple stab wounds.
Neck snapped.

00:22.356 --> 00:24.292
Pervert's at it again.

00:24.325 --> 00:25.626
[sirens]

00:25.659 --> 00:27.595
It's about time
the canine unit got here.

00:30.598 --> 00:32.766
Detectives,
got another Jane Doe.

00:32.800 --> 00:33.834
Same M.O.
as the others.

00:33.867 --> 00:36.570
