clean up his mess.

00:43.777 --> 00:45.179
Go get him, Angus.

00:45.213 --> 00:46.747
Come on, find the scent.

00:49.217 --> 00:52.353
Hey, bloody corpse over here.

00:52.386 --> 00:54.222
Stupid mutt can't even
hit his mark.

00:54.255 --> 00:55.423
