00:55.456 --> 00:56.690
Reset!

00:56.724 --> 00:59.360
Tony, find what's-his-name,
the trainer.

00:59.393 --> 01:00.761
His dog just
ruined my shot.

01:00.794 --> 01:02.830
I need a 20
on the dog wrangler.

01:02.863 --> 01:04.265
What's up with this dog?

01:04.298 --> 01:05.699
