01:11.172 --> 01:13.341
Jessie?

01:13.374 --> 01:15.309
Jess, you okay?

01:15.343 --> 01:16.410
Jessie!

01:18.346 --> 01:20.214
Jessie!

01:20.248 --> 01:21.415
Franco Marquez,

01:21.449 --> 01:23.617
executive producer
of Girl, Undercover.

01:23.651 --> 01:25.453
That's Jessie.
She's my star.

01:25.486 --> 01:26.854
What happened?

01:26.887 --> 01:28.322
Looks like the perp
bashed her head

01:28.356 --> 01:29.357
