and raped her.

01:29.390 --> 01:30.591
(Fin)
She gonna be okay?

01:30.624 --> 01:31.692
Pupils are reactive.

01:31.725 --> 01:33.327
She's responding
to painful stimuli,

01:33.361 --> 01:34.828
but the ER
will have to scan her.

01:34.862 --> 01:37.231
What just happened?

01:37.265 --> 01:39.167
(Marquez)
I found her lying
right here on the floor.

01:39.200 --> 01:40.701
Who has access
to Jessie's trailer?

01:40.734 --> 01:42.803
Just the crew.

01:42.836 --> 01:43.904
Security has strict orders.

01:43.937 --> 01:46.207
No one's allowed on the set
unless they work for me.

01:46.240 --> 01:48.142
Anyone on the crew
have a problem with Jessie?

01:48.176 --> 01:50.911
No, we've been together
for three seasons.

01:50.944 --> 01:54.215
I know it sounds cornball,
but we're like family.

01:54.248 --> 01:55.316
(Fin)
What's all this?

01:55.349 --> 01:58.686
Jessie the Slut?
Teen Tramp?

01:58.719 --> 01:59.853
Rag magazines.

01:59.887 --> 02:01.322
They have a field day

02:01.355 --> 02:03.191
