wears something slinky.

02:03.224 --> 02:05.359
She ain't wearing
much of anything here.

02:05.393 --> 02:06.360
"Jezebel Jessie"?

02:06.394 --> 02:07.695
It's just words.

02:07.728 --> 02:09.430
Sticks and stones, right?

02:09.463 --> 02:11.265
(Stabler)
