03:15.696 --> 03:17.331
Any chance she took
those pills herself?

03:17.365 --> 03:19.600
Well, she didn't
give herself the contusion.

03:19.633 --> 03:20.601
Okay, so he drugs her,

03:20.634 --> 03:22.370
