was gonna start spinning.

03:30.978 --> 03:32.646
Why are you doing this to me?

03:32.680 --> 03:33.714
I don't know!

03:33.747 --> 03:35.716
Ms. Dawning.
Detective Stabler--

03:35.749 --> 03:37.418
I don't remember
anything, okay?

03:37.451 --> 03:38.686
I went to take a nap
in my trailer,

03:38.719 --> 03:40.388
next thing I know,
I wake up here.

03:40.421 --> 03:41.922
You have anything to drink
before you fell asleep?

03:41.955 --> 03:43.691
Just a diet soda
with lemon on the set.

03:43.724 --> 03:44.692
Who gave it to you?

03:44.725 --> 03:45.693
I don't know.

03:45.726 --> 03:46.760
It was just by my chair.

03:46.794 --> 03:47.828
Where the hell
are my shoes?!

03:47.861 --> 03:48.862
