37:40.759 --> 37:43.362
of your crusade
to rid the world of filth?

37:43.395 --> 37:46.865
People like BJ
have taken over television...

37:46.898 --> 37:49.368
the Internet, movies, music.

37:49.401 --> 37:51.069
And you want to silence them.

37:51.102 --> 37:53.505
I want my children
to have a childhood.

37:53.539 --> 37:55.541
I'm all alone
raising two kids,

37:55.574 --> 37:57.543
and it is almost impossible

37:57.576 --> 37:59.044
to keep that obscenity
away from them.

37:59.077 --> 38:02.448
And that justifies
shooting BJ?

38:04.750 --> 38:07.786
That man...

38:07.819 --> 38:10.489
took away
everything I believe in.

38:10.522 --> 38:15.827
He took away my family.

38:15.861 --> 38:19.765
My baby's future.

38:19.798 --> 38:21.367
And I had to stop him.

38:21.400 --> 38:23.902
I didn't know
what else to do.

38:36.748 --> 38:38.717
You lose yet?

38:38.750 --> 38:40.118
I'm working on it.

38:40.151 --> 38:41.787
Told you.

38:41.820 --> 38:43.755
You put Carolyn Spencer
next to BJ,

38:43.789 --> 38:44.690
she's gonna look like
Mother Theresa.

38:44.723 --> 38:47.092
It's an extreme
emotional disturbance case.

38:47.125 --> 38:48.660
I can't object
to the defense

38:48.694 --> 38:50.429
painting a picture
of the heartbroken mother.

38:50.462 --> 38:52.831
You want to convince the jury
Carolyn's guilty,

38:52.864 --> 38:55.501
show them she's responsible
for her actions,

38:55.534 --> 38:57.002
just like Danny was.

38:57.035 --> 38:58.537
Wish I could
put him on the stand,

38:58.570 --> 39:00.005
but he won't say boo
against her.

39:00.038 --> 39:02.007
Maybe he'll change his mind
when he hears about this.

39:02.040 --> 39:03.975
Got a hold
of Mom's phone records.

39:04.009 --> 39:05.744
Look who his mom
was talking to

39:05.777 --> 39:07.513
right before
she shot BJ.

39:09.848 --> 39:11.082
Why are we here?

39:11.116 --> 39:13.419
People's exhibits
eight and nine.

39:13.452 --> 39:14.986
The defense hasn't
gone over those documents.

39:15.020 --> 39:16.588
You will.

39:16.622 --> 39:18.557
We're just waiting
on one more person.

39:18.590 --> 39:20.492
And here he is.

39:20.526 --> 39:22.861
Danny...

39:22.894 --> 39:25.130
Hey.

39:25.163 --> 39:27.466
(defense attorney)
Why is he here?

39:27.499 --> 39:29.735
So I can convince him
to testify against his mother.

39:29.768 --> 39:32.137
I told you no way.

39:32.170 --> 39:33.672
People's Exhibit Eight.

39:33.705 --> 39:35.941
A copy
of Carolyn Spencer's LUDS,

39:35.974 --> 39:37.175
showing two phone calls

39:37.208 --> 39:39.945
to NICE vice president
James Willoughby

39:39.978 --> 39:41.880
on the afternoon
BJ Cameron was shot.

39:41.913 --> 39:43.549
Is there a point
to all this?

39:43.582 --> 39:44.883
People's Exhibit Nine.

39:44.916 --> 39:46.552
Copy of the check
the New York Ledger

39:46.585 --> 39:48.119
wrote to the same
James Willoughby

39:48.153 --> 39:51.823
as payment for pictures
of BJ Cameron's shooting.

39:53.992 --> 39:57.128
Mr. Willoughby
took those pictures?

39:57.162 --> 39:59.798
You asked him to.

39:59.831 --> 40:02.768
Bet you didn't think anyone
would find out, did you?

40:02.801 --> 40:04.836
I don't know
what you're talking about.

40:04.870 --> 40:05.871
You talked to him

40:05.904 --> 40:07.939
for twenty minutes
that afternoon.

40:07.973 --> 40:09.841
You told him to take pictures
of the shooting.

40:09.875 --> 40:11.543
No, I didn't.

40:11.577 --> 40:14.846
We'll see what Mr. Willoughby
says on the witness stand.

40:14.880 --> 40:17.048
He'll say the same thing.

40:17.082 --> 40:18.717
You planned it?

40:18.750 --> 40:21.753
Why?

40:21.787 --> 40:23.722
So the whole world
would see her

40:23.755 --> 40:25.791
as a martyr
for her cause.

40:27.659 --> 40:29.094
It was just
a publicity stunt?

40:29.127 --> 40:31.129
No!
No, don't listen to her.

40:31.162 --> 40:32.964
I did it for you.

40:35.100 --> 40:38.036
You're so full of it.

40:43.241 --> 40:44.743
I want to testify.

40:46.745 --> 40:47.913
I'll tell them
she didn't shoot BJ

40:47.946 --> 40:49.114
because of me.

40:49.147 --> 40:50.248
I'll tell them
she just wanted

40:50.281 --> 40:51.817
to get her stupid crusade
on the news.

40:51.850 --> 40:52.884
No.

40:52.918 --> 40:56.021
I did it because
I love you.

40:58.624 --> 41:00.659
I wanna go back
to my cell.

41:00.692 --> 41:02.093
Danny, no!

41:02.127 --> 41:05.130
Wait, Danny, plea--
Danny!

41:09.167 --> 41:10.869
Last chance.

41:10.902 --> 41:11.937
I'll drop
the attempted murder

41:11.970 --> 41:13.972
if she pleads guilty
to assault.

41:18.944 --> 41:20.846
I didn't
do anything wrong.

41:20.879 --> 41:22.514
And this has all

41:22.548 --> 41:23.782
been fascinating,

41:23.815 --> 41:26.184
but it doesn't
prove a thing.

41:27.819 --> 41:30.021
Then we'll let a jury decide.

41:36.628 --> 41:39.130
(judge)
Mr. Foreman, you've been
deliberating for two weeks.

41:39.164 --> 41:40.999
What's the division of votes?

41:41.032 --> 41:42.634
Six to six, your honor.

41:42.668 --> 41:43.869
Is there any chance,
with more time,

41:43.902 --> 41:45.103
you could reach a verdict?

41:45.136 --> 41:46.171
We've tried.

41:46.204 --> 41:48.306
We're deadlocked.

41:48.339 --> 41:50.776
Then I have no choice
but to declare a mistrial.

41:50.809 --> 41:52.711
Yes!

41:52.744 --> 41:54.613
The defendant's bail
is continued

41:54.646 --> 41:57.082
pending the people's decision
for a retrial.

41:57.115 --> 41:59.217
[gavel pounds]

42:10.996 --> 42:11.930
How do you deadlock

42:11.963 --> 42:13.899
with a mountain of evidence
in front of you?

42:13.932 --> 42:16.201
The jury thought
BJ deserved what he got.

42:16.234 --> 42:18.570
He flapped his mouth
on the radio.

42:18.604 --> 42:20.305
She picked up a gun
and shot him!

42:20.338 --> 42:22.040
There's no question
who broke the law here.

42:22.073 --> 42:23.775
No, but after
hearing BJ on the stand,

42:23.809 --> 42:25.577
half the jury would have
done what Carolyn did.

42:25.611 --> 42:26.978
[knock knock]

42:27.012 --> 42:28.580
Gotta hear this.

42:32.618 --> 42:35.921
BJ's been in full rant mode
for the last five minutes.

42:35.954 --> 42:40.058
(BJ, on radio)
Carolyn Spencer's not just
a bitch with a capital "C,"

42:40.091 --> 42:41.893
she's a fascist who should be
tried and fried

42:41.927 --> 42:43.929
for crimes
against democracy.

42:43.962 --> 42:47.098
Strap her into old sparky
and shoot a million volts

42:47.132 --> 42:48.867
through that Nazi
brain of hers!

42:48.900 --> 42:50.869
Think they'll let me
pull the switch?

42:50.902 --> 42:53.138
And you wonder why people
want that guy to shut up.

42:55.073 --> 42:56.975
No one's forcing them
to listen.

42:57.008 --> 42:58.576
(BJ)
Let me tell you,
that woman is just--

